text = "When the Mushroom Kingdom’s famous Italian plumber binged on a patch of experimental \"Mega-Shrooms,\" he didn't gain super strength; instead, he transformed into a snoring, pizza-scented stone statue just as Bowser’s airships darkened the sky. With the kingdom in a panic and the hero literally petrified, Sinfanii stepped forward, calm and composed"

